location.fullValue: The Aurora Plan, Sendero at Pioneer Meadows

data.description: A World of Living!!! Custom Home with the Largest Panoramic Views!   Check out this 5/3.5/3 Car Garage with over 3,300 Square Feet.   Features: A Stunning New Stucco Exterior, New LVP Flooring and Baseboard, New Paint Inside & Out, Oversized Primary Bedroom Downstairs has Roman Tub and 2 walk-in Closets, Also a Second En suite Bedroom Upstairs with a View Deck, New Vanity & Hardware. Private Covered Patio with Hot Tub, Huge Paver Patio Prepped for your Pergola or Covering. Most Of The Home Features New Windows, Large Loft On The Second Floor, Exterior Recessed Lighting Around The Home w Christmas Receptacle Boxes, Pellet Stove, Fire Pit, Central Heat & A/C, 1.18 Acre Lot for all your toys or Horses, No HOA. Home Warranty good through 2027.
